OL,5, The energy regulator has said it has   
OL,6, seen "troubling signs" that suppliers  
OL,7, may have been increasing direct debit  
OL,8, payments by "more than is necessary".  
OL,10,FOfgem said it was concerned that firms 
OL,11,Fmay be directing customers to energy   
OL,12,Fdeals that aren't in their "best       
OL,13,Finterest".                             
OL,15,FIt comes as households face significant
OL,16,Fincreases in their energy bills.       
OL,18,FOn 1 April, yearly bills increased by  
OL,19,Fan average of #693 for about 18 million
OL,20,Fhouseholds on standard tariffs.        
